      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUSSIE WOOD (4) is yet to break through in 16 starts but has run a number of placings. Finished sixth (26.20) at Grafton latest but tends to run well here despite having never won. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Ready to return to form. HARA'S MOSAIC (2) jumped from the middle and safely held on debut at this track over 520m (31.11). Can find the frame this time. SWEET RIPPLE (1) has her first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Can measure up. NO REIGNS (6) is a Michael Lalicz-trained newcomer by Feral Franky out of Ripple Reign. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability.",
